    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system to achieve its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system overhauled with uprated seals, and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains taut, featuring factory-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers. With flawless Carbon Black metallic paint and a pristine Nappa leather interior, this is a mechanically sorted, collector-quality specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
