      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in a stunning Guards Red finish. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The factory wheels are flawless, wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Inside, the Black leather interior remains firm and smells like new, showing no signs of bolster wear, carpet staining, or aging. Every feature, from the Bose Surround Sound system to the heated adaptive sport seats and PCM navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, boasting a full Porsche dealership service history with all records included. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the very best and refuses to compromise on condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
